ha]], [[Qatar]] was held on 8 December at the Lusail Shooting Range.\n\n==Schedule==\n<small>All times are Arabia Standard Time ([[UTC+03:00]])</small>\n{|class = \"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! width=220|Date\n! width=50|Time\n! width=150|Event\n|-\n| Friday, 8 December 2006 || 08:00 || bgcolor=ffffcc|Final\n|}\n\n== Records ==\n{{Asian Games Record Shooting 2\n| world_athlete = {{flagathlete|[[Afanasijs Kuzmins]]|URS}}\n| world_mark    = 590\n| world_place   = [[Zagreb]], [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|Yugoslavia]]\n| world_date    = 15 July 1989\n| Asian_athlete = {{flagathlete|[[Park Byung-taek]]|KOR|1997}}\n| Asian_mark    = 590\n| Asian_place   = [[Lahti]], [[Finland]]\n| Asian_date    = 14 July 2002\n| Games_athlete = {{flagIOC2athlete|[[Park Byung-taek]]|KOR|1990 Asian Games}}\n| Games_mark    = 589\n| Games_place   = [[Beijing]], [[China]]\n| Games_date    = 29 September 1990\n}}\n\n==Results==\n;Legend\n*'''DNS''' \u2014 Did not start\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!rowspan=2 width=40|Rank\n!rowspan=2 width=250|Athlete\n!colspan=3|Precision\n!colspan=3|Rapid\n!rowspan=2 width=50|Total\n!rowspan=2 width=40|S-off\n!rowspan=2 width=45|Notes\n|-\n!width=30|1\n!width=30|2\n!width=30|3\n!width=30|1\n!width=30|2\n!width=30|3\n|-\n|{{Gold1}}||align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Jaspal Rana]]|IND|2006 Asian Games}}||98||98||98||100||98||98||'''590'''|| ||{{AsianGR|shooting}}\n|-\n|{{Silver2}}||align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Liu Guohui]]|CHN|2006 Asian Games}}||95||99||95||99||99||100||'''587'''|| ||\n|-\n|{{Bronze3}}||align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Jakkrit Panichpatikum]]|THA|2006 Asian Games}}||96||99||98||99||95||99||'''586'''|| ||\n|-\n| 4 || align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Park Byung-taek]]|KOR|2006 Asian Games}}||96||97||95||99||97||100||'''584'''|| ||\n|-\n| 5 || align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Ho\u00e0ng Xu\u00e2n Vinh]]|VIE|2006 Asian Games}}||97||97||96||94||100||98||'''582'''|| ||\n|-\n| 6 || align=left|{{flagIOC