ov]]|UZB|2006 Asian Games}} ||98||95||95||95||98||92||'''573'''|| ||\n|-\n| 22|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Liu Zhongsheng]]|CHN|2006 Asian Games}} ||96||97||97||91||95||96||'''572'''|| ||\n|-\n| 23|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Khalid Ahmed Mohamed]]|BRN|2006 Asian Games}} ||96||97||96||94||93||95||'''571'''|| ||\n|-\n| 24|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Ryu Myong-yon]]|PRK|2006 Asian Games}} ||98||97||98||92||93||93||'''571'''|| ||\n|-\n| 25|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Mohammad Zein]]|SYR|2006 Asian Games}} ||92||92||94||95||96||99||'''568'''|| ||\n|-\n| 26|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Hasli Izwan]]|MAS|2006 Asian Games}} ||93||92||90||99||98||96||'''568'''|| ||\n|-\n| 27|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Said Al-Hasani]]|OMA|2006 Asian Games}} ||94||94||94||94||97||95||'''568'''|| ||\n|-\n| 28|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Hadi Al-Qahtani]]|KSA|2006 Asian Games}} ||93||98||99||91||94||93||'''568'''|| ||\n|-\n| 29|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Vladimir Issachenko]]|KAZ|2006 Asian Games}} ||96||97||97||94||91||93||'''568'''|| ||\n|-\n| 30|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Opas Ruengpanyawut]]|THA|2006 Asian Games}} ||97||92||94||92||98||94||'''567'''|| ||\n|-\n| 31|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Ebrahim Barkhordari]]|IRI|2006 Asian Games}} ||92||95||95||95||97||92||'''566'''|| ||\n|-\n| 32|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Zafer Al-Qahtani]]|QAT|2006 Asian Games}} ||90||96||94||95||96||94||'''565'''|| ||\n|-\n| 33|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Irshad Ali]]|PAK|2006 Asian Games}} ||96||97||92||95||93||92||'''565'''|| ||\n|-\n| 34|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Muhammad Boota (sport shooter)|Muhammad Boota]]|PAK|2006 Asian Games}} ||93||92||96||93||93||97||'''564'''|| ||\n|-\n| 35|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Maed Al-Gazi]]|QAT|2006 Asian Games}} ||94||96||92||90||94||97||'''563'''|| ||\n|-\n| 36|| align=left|{{flagIOC2athlete|[[Adib Issa]]|SYR|2006 Asian Games}} ||96||94||91||95||89||97||'''562'''|| ||\n|-\n| 37|| align=left|{{flagIOC2